"Whether you're a Fortune 500, a startup, or anything in between, rest easy knowing your data is safe, and meet your compliance targets with our comprehensive security tools.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Whether you're a Fortune 500, a startup, or anything in between, rest easy knowing your data is safe, and meet your compliance targets with our comprehensive security tools.\",\"de-DE\":\"Egal, ob Sie ein Fortune-500-Unternehmen, ein Start-up oder irgendwas dazwischen sind: Sie können sich ganz entspannt zurücklehnen, denn mit unseren umfassenden Sicherheitstools schützen Sie Ihre Daten und erfüllen Ihre Compliance-Vorgaben.\",\"ko-KR\":\"포춘지 선정 500대 기업도 스타트업도, Vimeo의 포괄적인 보안 도구를 통해 데이터를 안전하게 보호하고 목표 규정 준수를 달성하세요.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Seja você uma empresa da Fortune 500, uma startup ou de qualquer tamanho, tenha a tranquilidade de saber que seus dados estão seguros e cumprem suas metas de conformidade com nossas abrangentes ferramentas de segurança.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Que vous soyez une entreprise du Fortune 500, une startup ou toute autre organisation, ayez la certitude que vos données sont en sécurité et atteignez vos objectifs en matière de conformité grâce à nos outils de sécurité complets.\",\"es\":\"Tanto si es una empresa de Fortune 500, una startup o una organización de otro tipo, descanse tranquilo sabiendo que sus datos están seguros y logre sus objetivos de cumplimiento con nuestras herramientas de seguridad integrales.\",\"ja-JP\":\"スタートアップからフォーチュン500企業まで、誰でも安心して利用できる包括的なセキュリティツールでデータを保護し、コンプライアンスの目標を達成できます。\"},\"Better Way To Work Guide\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Better Way To Work Guide\",\"de-DE\":\"Better Way To Work Guide\",\"ko-KR\":\"Better Way To Work Guide\",\"pt-BR\":\"Better Way To Work Guide\",\"fr-FR\":\"Better Way To Work Guide\",\"ja-JP\":\"より良い作業のためのガイド\",\"es\":\"Better Way To Work Guide\"},\"Vermicular's video investment boosts global reach and creates reusable marketing assets.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Vermicular's video investment boosts global reach and creates reusable marketing assets.\",\"de-DE\":\"Die Videoinvestition von Vermicular steigert die globale Reichweite und schafft wiederverwendbare Marketingressourcen.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vermicular는 동영상 제작에 투자함으로써 글로벌 도달 범위를 확대하고 재사용 가능한 마케팅 자산을 창출합니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"O investimento em vídeo da Vermicular aumenta o alcance global e cria ativos de marketing reutilizáveis.\",\"fr-FR\":\"L’investissement vidéo de Vermicular renforce sa portée mondiale et génère des ressources marketing réutilisables.\",\"ja-JP\":\"Vermicularは動画への投資により、世界的なリーチを拡大し、再利用可能なマーケティング資産を作成しています。\",\"es\":\"La inversión en video de Vermicular impulsa el alcance global y crea activos de marketing reutilizables.\"},\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\",\"de-DE\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\",\"ko-KR\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\",\"pt-BR\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\",\"fr-FR\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\",\"ja-JP\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\",\"es\":\"Link to Better Way to Work guide\"},\"Add team members using Vimeo's video management settings to control access for different groups, including brand design and product marketing.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Add team members using Vimeo's video management settings to control access for different groups, including brand design and product marketing.\",\"de-DE\":\"Fügen Sie Teammitglieder hinzu, indem Sie die Videoverwaltungseinstellungen von Vimeo verwenden, um den Zugriff für verschiedene Gruppen zu steuern, einschließlich Markendesign und Produktmarketing.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo의 동영상 관리 설정에서 팀원을 추가하여 브랜드 디자인과 제품 마케팅 등 다양한 팀의 액세스 권한을 제어할 수 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Adicione integrantes à equipe usando as configurações de gerenciamento de vídeo do Vimeo para controlar o acesso de diferentes grupos, incluindo design de marca e marketing de produto.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Ajoutez des collaborateurs en utilisant les paramètres de gestion vidéo de Vimeo pour contrôler l'accès de différents groupes, y compris la conception de la marque et le marketing produits.\",\"ja-JP\":\"Vimeoの動画管理設定を使用してチームメンバーを追加し、ブランドデザインや製品マーケティングなど、さまざまなグループのアクセスを制御。\",\"es\":\"Agrega miembros del equipo utilizando la configuración de gestión de video de Vimeo para controlar el acceso de diferentes grupos, incluido el diseño de marca y el marketing de productos.\"},\"Summer 2024 Release\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Summer 2024 Release\",\"de-DE\":\"Sommer-Release 2024\",\"ko-KR\":\"2024년 여름 출시\",\"pt-BR\":\"Lançamentos 3T de 2024\",\"fr-FR\":\"Version Été 2024\",\"ja-JP\":\"2024年夏のリリース\",\"es\":\"Lanzamiento del T3 2024\"},\"Choose exactly who can watch your video before it's even finished uploading. Share only with specific individuals, put it behind a password, or hide it from everyone but you.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Choose exactly who can watch your video before it's even finished uploading. Share only with specific individuals, put it behind a password, or hide it from everyone but you.\",\"de-DE\":\"Legen Sie genau fest, wer Ihr Video ansehen darf, noch bevor es überhaupt hochgeladen ist. Teilen Sie Ihr Video nur mit bestimmten Personen, sichern Sie es mit einem Kennwort oder machen Sie es nur für sich selbst sichtbar.\",\"ko-KR\":\"동영상 업로드가 완료되기 전, 해당 동영상을 시청할 수 있는 사람을 미리 지정할 수 있습니다. 지정된 개인에게 동영상을 공유하거나, 영상에 비밀번호를 설정하거나, 공개 범위를 비공개로 설정해 보세요.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Escolha exatamente quem pode ver seu vídeo antes mesmo de terminar de carregá-lo. Compartilhe apenas com pessoas específicas, coloque uma senha ou oculte para todos, menos você.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Sélectionnez qui peut regarder votre vidéo avant même qu'elle ne soit en ligne. Partagez-la uniquement avec les personnes de votre choix, protégez-la avec un mot de passe ou gardez-la à l'abri des regards.\",\"ja-JP\":\"アップロード完了前でも、動画にアクセスできるユーザーを選択できます。特定の人とだけ共有したり、パスワードで保護したり、自分以外の人に非表示にすることもできます。\",\"es\":\"Elija exactamente quién puede ver su video incluso antes de que termine de subirlo. Compártalo solo con determinadas personas, protéjalo con una contraseña u ocúltelo a todo el mundo excepto usted.\"},\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\",\"de-DE\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\",\"ja-JP\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\",\"es\":\"Explore new capabilities and exciting updates in our Summer 2024 Release.\"},\"Contact Support\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Contact Support\",\"de-DE\":\"Support kontaktieren\",\"ko-KR\":\"지원팀에 문의하기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Suporte\",\"fr-FR\":\"Contacter l'assistance\",\"ja-JP\":\"サポートへのお問い合わせ\",\"es\":\"Contactar al equipo de asistencia\"},\"Our customer support team is available to help 24/7. Enterprise members also receive dedicated account managers and a guaranteed uptime SLA.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Our customer support team is available to help 24/7. Enterprise members also receive dedicated account managers and a guaranteed uptime SLA.\",\"de-DE\":\"Unser Kundensupport steht Ihnen rund um die Uhr zur Seite. Enterprise-Mitglieder profitieren außerdem von der Unterstützung durch dedizierte Kundenbetreuer und einem SLA für garantierte Verfügbarkeit.\",\"ko-KR\":\"연중무휴 24시간 고객 지원이 제공됩니다. Enterprise 회원에게는 전담 계정 관리자와 보장된 업타임 SLA 또한 제공합니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Nossa equipe de suporte ao cliente está disponível para ajudar 24 horas por dia, 7 dias por semana. Quem assina o Enterprise também pode contar com uma equipe de gerentes de conta dedicada e um SLA de tempo de atividade garantido.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Notre équipe d'assistance client est disponible 24 h/24 et 7 j/7.   Les membres Entreprise bénéficient également de l'aide d'un responsable de compte attitré et d'une disponibilité garantie.\",\"ja-JP\":\"Vimeoのカスタマーサポートチームが24時間年中無休で対応。Enterpriseメンバーには、専用のアカウントマネージャーがつき、保証された稼働時間SLAが提供されます。\",\"es\":\"Nuestro equipo de asistencia al cliente está disponible las 24 horas, los 7 días de la semana. Los miembros de Enterprise también tienen acceso a administradores de cuentas especializados y a un ANS de tiempo de actividad garantizado.\"},\"Get Started\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Get Started\",\"de-DE\":\"Los geht's\",\"ko-KR\":\"시작하기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Começar\",\"fr-FR\":\"Démarrer\",\"ja-JP\":\"利用を開始\",\"es\":\"Empezar\"},\"Log In\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Log In\",\"de-DE\":\"Einloggen\",\"ko-KR\":\"로그인\",\"pt-BR\":\"Entrar\",\"fr-FR\":\"Se connecter\",\"ja-JP\":\"ログイン\",\"es\":\"Iniciar sesión\"},\"open main menu\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"open main menu\",\"de-DE\":\"open main menu\",\"ko-KR\":\"open main menu\",\"pt-BR\":\"open main menu\",\"fr-FR\":\"open main menu\",\"ja-JP\":\"open main menu\",\"es\":\"open main menu\"},\"close main menu\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"close main menu\",\"de-DE\":\"close main menu\",\"ko-KR\":\"close main menu\",\"pt-BR\":\"close main menu\",\"fr-FR\":\"close main menu\",\"ja-JP\":\"close main menu\",\"es\":\"close main menu\"},\"go back to main menu\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"go back to main menu\",\"de-DE\":\"go back to main menu\",\"pt-BR\":\"go back to main menu\",\"ko-