BR\":\"Aplicativos customizados nas plataformas que seu público usa diariamente\",\"fr-FR\":\"Des applications personnalisées sur les plateformes que vos spectateurs utilisent au quotidien\",\"ja-JP\":\"視聴者が毎日使用するプラットフォーム上のカスタムアプリ\",\"es\":\"Aplicaciones personalizadas en las plataformas que tus espectadores usan todos los días\"},\"Learn More\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Learn More\",\"de-DE\":\"Mehr erfahren\",\"ko-KR\":\"자세히 보기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Saiba mais\",\"fr-FR\":\"En savoir plus\",\"ja-JP\":\"詳細はこちら\",\"es\":\"Más información\"},\"The three-time Staff Picked director shares his deeply personal, powerful short films with Vimeo.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"The three-time Staff Picked director shares his deeply personal, powerful short films with Vimeo.\",\"de-DE\":\"Der Filmproduzent, dessen Filme schon dreimal als Staff Picks ausgewählt wurden, teilt seine sehr persönlichen und bewegenden Kurzfilme über Vimeo.\",\"ko-KR\":\"세 번 연속 스태프 픽으로 선정된 영화감독 Morgan Cooper가 Vimeo를 통해 강렬하면서도 지극히 개인적인 단편 영화를 공유합니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"O diretor três vezes escolhido como Staff Pick compartilha seus curtas-metragens profundamente pessoais e impactantes com o Vimeo.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Sélectionné à trois reprises dans les Staff Picks de Vimeo, le réalisateur partage ses courts métrages puissants et profondément personnels avec Vimeo.\",\"ja-JP\":\"3度にわたりスタッフピックに選ばれた監督が、極めて私的でパワフルな短編映画をVimeoで公開します。\",\"es\":\"Este director destacado, tres veces elegido por el personal, comparte sus cortometrajes profundamente personales e impactantes con Vimeo.\"},\"Password\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Password\",\"de-DE\":\"Kennwort\",\"ko-KR\":\"비밀번호\",\"pt-BR\":\"Senha\",\"fr-FR\":\"Mot de passe \",\"ja-JP\":\"パスワード\",\"es\":\"Contraseña\"},\"See plans\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"See plans\",\"de-DE\":\"Tarife ansehen\",\"ko-KR\":\"요금제 보기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Ver planos\",\"fr-FR\":\"Abonnements\",\"ja-JP\":\"プランを見る\",\"es\":\"Ver los planes\"},\"Stream your events live, or host them on-demand. Our tools make it easy to share your content with the world.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Stream your events live, or host them on-demand. Our tools make it easy to share your content with the world.\",\"de-DE\":\"Streamen Sie Ihre Events live oder hosten Sie sie on-demand. Mit unseren Tools können Sie Ihre Inhalte ganz einfach mit der ganzen Welt teilen.\",\"ko-KR\":\"이벤트를 라이브 스트리밍하거나 온디맨드로 호스팅하세요. Vimeo의 도구를 활용하면 전 세계에 콘텐츠를 손쉽게 공유할 수 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Transmita seus eventos ao vivo ou hospede-os sob demanda. Nossas ferramentas facilitam o compartilhamento do seu conteúdo com o mundo.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Diffusez vos événements en direct ou organisez-les à la demande. Nos outils vous permettent de partager facilement votre contenu avec le monde entier.\",\"ja-JP\":\"イベントのライブストリーミングや、オンデマンドでのホスティングなど、Vimeoのツールなら、コンテンツを世界各地の視聴者と簡単に共有できます。\",\"es\":\"Transmita sus eventos en vivo o alójelos on-demand. Nuestras herramientas le permiten compartir fácilmente su contenido con el resto del mundo.\"},\"Join Vimeo\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Join Vimeo\",\"de-DE\":\"Registriere dich bei Vimeo\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo 가입\",\"pt-BR\":\"Cadastre-se no Vimeo\",\"fr-FR\":\"S'inscrire à Vimeo\",\"ja-JP\":\"Vimeoに登録\",\"es\":\"Unirse a Vimeo\"},\"Try it free\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Try it free\",\"de-DE\":\"Kostenlos testen\",\"ko-KR\":\"무료 체험\",\"pt-BR\":\"Teste gratuitamente\",\"fr-FR\":\"Essai gratuit\",\"ja-JP\":\"無料でお試し\",\"es\":\"Pruébalo gratis\"},\"Want to learn more about live? Sign up for our weekly demo with live Q\u0026A.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Want to learn more about live? Sign up for our weekly demo with live Q\u0026A.\",\"de-DE\":\"Möchtest du mehr zum Thema Livestreaming erfahren? Melde dich für unsere wöchentliche Demo mit Live-Fragerunden an.\",\"ko-KR\":\"라이브에 대해 더 알고 싶으신가요? 실시간 Q/A가 포함된 주간 데모를 신청하세요.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Quer saber mais sobre transmissões ao vivo? Inscreva-se em nossa demonstração semanal com sessões de perguntas e respostas ao vivo.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Vous souhaitez en savoir plus sur les abonnements live ? Inscrivez-vous pour participer à notre démo hebdomadaire avec session de questions-réponses en direct.\",\"ja-JP\":\"ライブ配信にご興味がある場合は、ライブ質問セッションのある毎週のデモセッションにご登録ください。\",\"es\":\"¿Quieres conocer más acerca de la transmisión en vivo? Inscríbete en nuestra demostración semanal con una sesión de preguntas y respuestas en vivo.\"},\"Events\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Events\",\"de-DE\":\"Events\",\"ko-KR\":\"이벤트\",\"pt-BR\":\"Eventos\",\"fr-FR\":\"Événements\",\"ja-JP\":\"イベント\",\"es\":\"Eventos\"},\"Contact our team\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Contact our team\",\"de-DE\":\"Unser Team kontaktieren\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo 팀에 문의\",\"pt-BR\":\"Fale conosco\",\"fr-FR\":\"Contacter notre équipe\",\"ja-JP\":\"チームに問い合わせる\",\"es\":\"Contactar a nuestro equipo\"},\"Vimeo virtual venues platform with three main speakers who have large profile picture bubbles and an audience of smaller profile pictures below showing the attendees.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Vimeo virtual venues platform with three main speakers who have large profile picture bubbles and an audience of smaller profile pictures below showing the attendees.\",\"de-DE\":\"Virtuelle Veranstaltungsplattform von Vimeo mit drei Hauptreferenten, die große Profilbilder in Sprechblasen haben, und einem Publikum mit kleineren Profilbildern darunter, die die Teilnehmer zeigen.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo 가상 광장 플랫폼에는 큰 프로필 사진 버블로 강조된 세 명의 주요 발표자와 그 아래 참석자를 나타내는 작은 프로필 사진으로 이루어진 청중이 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Plataforma de venues virtuais do Vimeo com três palestrantes principais e com fotos de perfil em balões grandes e um público composto de fotos de perfil menores abaixo, mostrando os participantes.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Plateforme de rencontres virtuelles Vimeo avec trois intervenants principaux qui ont de grandes bulles d'images de profil et, en dessous, un public de participants représenté avec de plus petites images de profil.\",\"ja-JP\":\"3人の主要講演者が大きなプロフィール写真の吹き出しで表示され、その下に参加者らが小さなプロフィールで表示されたVimeoのバーチャル会場プラットフォーム。\",\"es\":\"Plataforma de venues virtuales de Vimeo con tres oradores principales que tienen grandes burbujas de fotos de perfil y una audiencia de fotos de perfil más pequeñas debajo que muestran a los asistentes.\"},\"Sign up\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Sign up\",\"de-DE\":\"Anmelden\",\"ko-KR\":\"가입하기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Inscreva-se\",\"fr-FR\":\"S'inscrire\",\"ja-JP\":\"サインアップ\",\"es\":\"Registrarse\"},\"Sales:\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Sales:\",\"de-DE\":\"Vertrieb:\",\"ko-KR\":\"영업팀:\",\"pt-BR\":\"Vendas:\",\"fr-FR\":\"Ventes :\",\"ja-JP\":\"営業：\",\"es\":\"Ventas:\"},\"Vimeo OTT services allowing members to set purchase options for their video subscription channels, with subscribers having the choice between an annual or monthly payment.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Vimeo OTT services allowing members to set purchase options for their video subscription channels, with subscribers having the choice between an annual or monthly payment.\",\"de-DE\":\"Die Services von Vimeo OTT ermöglichen es den Mitgliedern, Kaufoptionen für ihre Video-Abonnementkanäle festzulegen, wobei die Abonnenten die Wahl zwischen einer jährlichen oder monatlichen Zahlung haben.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo OTT 서비스를 통해 회원은 동영상 구독 채널에 대한 결제 옵션을 설정할 수 있으며, 구독자는 연간 또는 월간 결제 중에서 선택할 수 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Serviços do Vimeo OTT, que permitem que os membros definam opções de compra nos seus canais de assinatura de vídeo, com os assinantes podendo escolher entre o pagamento anual ou mensal.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Les services Vimeo OT