oom-Aufzeichnungen und andere Dateien enthalten.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo 동영상 라이브러리는 프라이버시 설정, 팀 설정, Zoom 녹화본 및 기타 파일이 포함된 카테고리별 폴더가 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Biblioteca de vídeos do Vimeo com configurações de privacidade e de equipe, e pastas categorizadas que incluem gravações do Zoom e outros arquivos.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Vidéothèque Vimeo avec paramètres de confidentialité, paramètres d'équipe et dossiers par catégories comprenant les enregistrements Zoom et d'autres fichiers.\",\"ja-JP\":\"プライバシー設定、チーム設定、Zoom録画やその他のファイルが含まれ分類されたフォルダが揃ったVimeoの動画ライブラリ。\",\"es\":\"Videoteca de Vimeo con configuración de privacidad, configuración de equipo y carpetas clasificadas que incluyen grabaciones de Zoom y otros archivos.\"},\"Video tools to power any business\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Video tools to power any business\",\"de-DE\":\"Videotools für jedes Unternehmen\",\"ko-KR\":\"비즈니스 성과를 높이는 동영상 도구\",\"pt-BR\":\"Ferramentas de vídeo para impulsionar qualquer negócio\",\"fr-FR\":\"Des outils vidéo utiles à toute entreprise\",\"ja-JP\":\"あらゆるビジネスを強化する動画ツール\",\"es\":\"Herramientas de video para potenciar cualquier negocio\"},\"The video platform trusted by 287 million creatives, entrepreneurs, and businesses. Everything you need to create, manage, and share stunning videos.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"The video platform trusted by 287 million creatives, entrepreneurs, and businesses. Everything you need to create, manage, and share stunning videos.\",\"de-DE\":\"Die Videoplattform, der 287 Millionen Kreative, Entrepreneure und Unternehmen vertrauen. Alles, was Sie brauchen, um beeindruckende Videos zu erstellen, zu verwalten und zu teilen.\",\"ko-KR\":\"2억 8,700만 명의 크리에이티브 전문가, 기업가, 비즈니스가 신뢰하는 동영상 플랫폼입니다. 고품질 동영상을 제작, 관리, 공유하는 데 필요한 모든 것이 준비되어 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"A plataforma de vídeos de confiança de 287 milhões de criadores, empreendedores e empresas. Tudo o que você precisa para criar, gerenciar e compartilhar vídeos incríveis.\",\"fr-FR\":\"287 millions de professionnels de la vidéo, d'entrepreneurs et d'entreprises nous font confiance. Tout ce dont vous avez besoin pour créer, gérer et partager des vidéos d'une qualité exceptionnelle.\",\"ja-JP\":\"2億8,700万のクリエイター、起業家、企業から信頼されている動画プラットフォーム。高品質な動画の作成、管理、共有に必要なすべてが揃っています。\",\"es\":\"La plataforma de video en la que confían 287 millones de creativos, emprendedores y empresas. Todo lo que necesita para crear, gestionar y compartir videos asombrosos.\"},\"Streamline your workflow\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Streamline your workflow\",\"de-DE\":\"Arbeitsablauf optimieren\",\"ko-KR\":\"작업 과정을 능률화하세요\",\"pt-BR\":\"Otimize seu Fluxo de Trabalho\",\"fr-FR\":\"Simplifiez votre workflow\",\"ja-JP\":\"ワークフローを効率化\",\"es\":\"Agilice el flujo de trabajo\"},\"Video Management\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Video Management\",\"de-DE\":\"Videoverwaltung\",\"ko-KR\":\"동영상 관리\",\"pt-BR\":\"Gerenciamento de vídeo\",\"fr-FR\":\"Gestion vidéo\",\"ja-JP\":\"動画管理\",\"es\":\"Gestión de video\"},\"Find open positions\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Find open positions\",\"de-DE\":\"Freie Stellen finden\",\"ko-KR\":\"채용 분야\",\"pt-BR\":\"Encontrar vagas\",\"fr-FR\":\"Trouver des postes vacants\",\"ja-JP\":\"現在募集中の職種を探す\",\"es\":\"Encontrar puestos vacantes\"},\"Create free channel\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Create free channel\",\"de-DE\":\"Gratis Kanal erstellen\",\"ko-KR\":\"무료 채널\\n만들기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Criar um canal grátis\",\"fr-FR\":\"Créer une chaîne gratuite\",\"ja-JP\":\"無料チャンネルを作成\",\"es\":\"Crear un canal gratis\"},\"Host your videos with our HD, ad-free player. Wherever you embed or share them, your custom player design and branding will go with it.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Host your videos with our HD, ad-free player. Wherever you embed or share them, your custom player design and branding will go with it.\",\"de-DE\":\"Hosten Sie Ihre Videos in unserem werbefreien HD-Player. Egal, wo Sie Ihre Inhalte einbetten oder teilen: Ihr individuelles Playerdesign und Branding sind mit dabei.\",\"ko-KR\":\"광고 없는 HD 플레이어로 동영상을 호스팅하세요. 동영상을 임베드하거나 공유한 곳에도 커스텀 플레이어 디자인과 브랜딩이 그대로 적용됩니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Hospede seus vídeos com nosso player HD sem anúncios. Onde quer que você os incorpore ou compartilhe, o design e a identidade de marca do seu player customizado vão junto.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Hébergez vos vidéos sur notre player HD sans pubs. Où que vous intégriez ou partagiez vos vidéos, vous pourrez personnaliser votre player et y ajouter votre image de marque.\",\"ja-JP\":\"広告なしのHDプレーヤーで動画をホスティング。埋め込みや共有の場所に合わせて、カスタムプレーヤーのデザインやブランディングも可能です。\",\"es\":\"Aloje sus videos con nuestro reproductor HD sin anuncios. Dondequiera que los inserte o comparta, su diseño de reproductor personalizado y su marca los acompañarán.\"},\"Trusted by top brands.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Trusted by top brands.\",\"de-DE\":\"Führende Marken vertrauen uns\",\"ko-KR\":\"최고의 브랜드가 신뢰합니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Marcas líderes no mercado confiam em nós.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Le choix des grandes marques.\",\"ja-JP\":\"トップブランドから信頼されています。\",\"es\":\"Las mejores marcas confían en nosotros\"},\"Search for a role, city, category...\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Search for a role, city, category...\",\"de-DE\":\"Suche nach einer Stelle, Stadt, Kategorie …\",\"ko-KR\":\"역할, 도시, 카테고리 검색...\",\"pt-BR\":\"Busque por função, cidade, categoria…\",\"fr-FR\":\"Recherchez un poste, une ville, une catégorie…\",\"ja-JP\":\"職種、都市、カテゴリーを検索\",\"es\":\"Busca un puesto, una ciudad o una categoría...\"},\"New Releases\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"New Releases\",\"de-DE\":\"Neue Releases\",\"ko-KR\":\"새 출시 제품\",\"pt-BR\":\"Novos lançamentos\",\"fr-FR\":\"Nouvelles versions\",\"ja-JP\":\"新しいリリース\",\"es\":\"Nuevos lanzamientos\"},\"Platform\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Platform\",\"de-DE\":\"Plattform\",\"ko-KR\":\"플랫폼\",\"pt-BR\":\"Plataforma\",\"fr-FR\":\"Plateforme\",\"ja-JP\":\"プラットフォーム\",\"es\":\"Plataforma\"},\"Exporting Vimeo audio logs .csv files under the team management settings by selecting a date range from a calendar.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Exporting Vimeo audio logs .csv files under the team management settings by selecting a date range from a calendar.\",\"de-DE\":\"Exportieren von Vimeo-Audioprotokollen als CSV-Dateien unter den Einstellungen der Teamverwaltung durch Auswahl eines Datumsbereichs aus einem Kalender.\",\"ko-KR\":\"팀 관리 설정에서 달력을 사용하여 날짜 범위를 선택하면 Vimeo 오디오 로그를 CSV 파일로 내보낼 수 있습니다.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Exportação de arquivos .csv de registro de áudio do Vimeo nas configurações de gerenciamento de equipe selecionando um intervalo de datas em um calendário.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Exportation des fichiers .csv des journaux audio Vimeo dans les paramètres de gestion de l'équipe en sélectionnant une plage de dates dans un calendrier.\",\"ja-JP\":\"カレンダーから日付範囲を選択して、チーム管理設定でVimeoオーディオログの.csvファイルをエクスポート。\",\"es\":\"Exportación de archivos .csv de registros de audio de Vimeo en la configuración de administración del equipo seleccionando un rango de fechas de un calendario.\"},\"Team\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Team\",\"de-DE\":\"Team\",\"ko-KR\":\"팀\",\"pt-BR\":\"Equipe\",\"fr-FR\":\"Équipe\",\"ja-JP\":\"チーム\",\"es\":\"Equipo\"},\"Android\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Android\",\"de-DE\":\"Android\",\"ko-KR\":\"Android\",\"pt-BR\":\"Android\",\"fr-FR\":\"Android\",\"ja-JP\":\"Android\",\"es\":\"Android\"},\"Log out\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Log out\",\"de-DE\":\"Abmelden\",\"ko-KR\":\"로그아웃\",\"pt-BR\":\"Sair\",\"fr-FR\":\"Déconnexion\",\"ja-JP\":\"ログアウト\",\"es\":\"Cerrar sesión\"},\"Our advanced live and on-demand video analytics help you understand viewer behavior and help you make changes for better future performance.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Our advanced live and on-demand video analytics help you understand viewer behavior and help you make changes for better future performance.\",\"de-DE\":\"Mit unserer fortschrittlichen Live- und On-Demand-Videoanalytik können Sie das Zuschauerverhalten verstehen und Änderungen vornehmen, um die Performance zukünftiger Videos zu verbessern.\",\"ko-KR\":\"고급 라이브 및 온디맨드 동영상 분석 기능을 통해 시청자 행동 양상을 파악하고 여기에서 얻은 인사이트를 활용하여 퍼포먼스를 개선하세요.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Nossa análise de vídeo avançada, ao vivo e sob demanda, ajuda você a entender o comportamento do espectador e a fazer alterações para melhorar o desempenho futuro.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Nos statistiques avancées des streamings en direct et des vidéos à la demande vous aident à analyser le comportement de vos spectateurs et à apporter les changements nécessaires pour améliorer vos futures performances.\",\"ja-JP\":\"視聴者の行動を理解し、今後のパフォーマンス改善に役立つ動画分析データが、ライブとオンデマンド動画の両方で取得できます。\",\"es\":\"Nuestros análisis avanzados de video en vivo y on-demand lo ayudan a comprender el comportamiento de los espectadores y a hacer los cambios necesarios para lograr mejores resultados en el futuro.\"},\"Continue\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Continue\",\"de-DE\":\"Weiter\",\"ko-KR\":\"계속\",\"pt-BR\":\"Continuar\",\"fr-FR\":\"Continuer\",\"ja-JP\":\"次へ\",\"es\":\"Continuar\"},\"category\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"category\",\"de-DE\":\"Kategorie\",\"ko-KR\":\"카테고리\",\"pt-BR\":\"categoria\",\"fr-FR\":\"catégorie\",\"ja-JP\":\"カテゴリー\",\"es\":\"categoría\"},\"Role\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Role\",\"de-DE\":\"Rolle\",\"ko-KR\":\"역할\",\"pt-BR\":\"Função\",\"fr-FR\":\"Poste\",\"ja-JP\":\"職種\",\"es\":\"Puesto\"},\"Control access with SSO, domain whitelisting, and embed restrictions, and manage granular user permissions with SCIM.\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Control access with SSO, domain whitelisting, and embed restrictions, and manage granular user permissions with SCIM.\",\"de-DE\":\"Profitieren Sie von Zugangskontrollen mit SSO, Domain-Whitelisting und Einbettungsbeschränkungen und verwalten Sie Benutzerberechtigungen granular mit SCIM.\",\"ko-KR\":\"SSO, 도메인 허용 목록 및 임베드 제한으로 액세스를 제어하고, SCIM으로 세분화된 사용자 권한을 관리하세요.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Controle o acesso com autenticação única (SSO), listas de permissões de domínio e restrições de incorporação e gerencie permissões detalhadas de usuário com o SCIM.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Contrôlez les accès grâce à l'authentification unique, au filtrage des domaines autorisés et aux restrictions d'intégration, et gérez les autorisations des utilisateurs de manière précise avec le SCIM.\",\"ja-JP\":\"SSO、ドメインのホワイトリスト登録、埋め込み制限を使用してアクセスを制御し、SCIMを使用して詳細なユーザー権限を管理します。\",\"es\":\"Controle el acceso con SSO, agregando dominios a la lista blanca e insertando restricciones, y gestione permisos detallados de usuarios con SCIM.\"},\"Use cases\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Use cases\",\"de-DE\":\"Anwendungsfälle\",\"ko-KR\":\"이용 사례\",\"pt-BR\":\"Exemplos de uso\",\"fr-FR\":\"Cas d'utilisation\",\"ja-JP\":\"ユースケース\",\"es\":\"Casos de uso\"},\"Amazon Fire TV\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Amazon Fire TV\",\"de-DE\":\"Amazon Fire TV\",\"ko-KR\":\"Amazon Fire TV\",\"pt-BR\":\"Amazon Fire TV\",\"fr-FR\":\"Amazon Fire TV\",\"ja-JP\":\"Amazon Fire TV\",\"es\":\"Amazon Fire TV\"},\"Search for location\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Search for location\",\"de-DE\":\"Nach Ort suchen\",\"ko-KR\":\"위치 검색\",\"pt-BR\":\"Buscar por local\",\"fr-FR\":\"Rechercher un lieu\",\"ja-JP\":\"場所を検索\",\"es\":\"Busca una ubicación\"},\"Analytics\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Analytics\",\"de-DE\":\"Analytics\",\"ko-KR\":\"애널리틱스\",\"pt-BR\":\"Análises\",\"fr-FR\":\"Analyses\",\"ja-JP\":\"分析\",\"es\":\"Análisis\"},\"Your full suite of video tools\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Your full suite of video tools\",\"de-DE\":\"Ihr Videotool-Komplettpaket\",\"ko-KR\":\"나에게 필요한 동영상 도구 모음\",\"pt-BR\":\"Seu conjunto completo de ferramentas de vídeo\",\"fr-FR\":\"Votre suite complète d'outils vidéo\",\"ja-JP\":\"動画ツールをフルセットで\",\"es\":\"Su paquete completo de herramientas de video\"},\"Browse all integrations\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Browse all integrations\",\"de-DE\":\"Alle Integrationen durchsuchen\",\"ko-KR\":\"모든 통합 살펴보기\",\"pt-BR\":\"Navegar por todas as integrações\",\"fr-FR\":\"Parcourir toutes les intégrations\",\"ja-JP\":\"すべての統合を閲覧する\",\"es\":\"Explorar todas las integraciones\"},\"Product\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Product\",\"de-DE\":\"Produkt\",\"ko-KR\":\"제품\",\"pt-BR\":\"Produtos\",\"fr-FR\":\"Produit\",\"ja-JP\":\"プロダクト\",\"es\":\"Producto\"},\"Sign in\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Sign in\",\"de-DE\":\"Sign in\",\"ko-KR\":\"Sign in\",\"pt-BR\":\"Sign in\",\"fr-FR\":\"Sign in\",\"ja-JP\":\"Sign in\",\"es\":\"Sign in\"},\"Meet Vimeo Central: our secure, AI-powered video hub\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Meet Vimeo Central: our secure, AI-powered video hub\",\"de-DE\":\"Wir präsentieren Vimeo Central: unsere sichere, KI-gestützte Video-Plattform\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo의 안전한 AI 기반의 동영상 허브, Vimeo Central을 만나보세요\",\"pt-BR\":\"Conheça o Vimeo Central: nosso hub de vídeo seguro, movido a IA\",\"fr-FR\":\"Découvrez Vimeo Central : notre centre de vidéos sécurisé et alimenté par l'IA.\",\"ja-JP\":\"安全なAI搭載動画ハブ、Vimeo Centralをご紹介します\",\"es\":\"Conozca Vimeo Central: nuestro centro de video seguro y potenciado por IA\"},\"Privacy\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"Privacy\",\"de-DE\":\