e nuestra comunidad.\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"Default\":\"How Vimeo is approaching AI, plus a call for feedback from our community.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Como o Vimeo está abordando a IA e um pedido de feedback para nossa comunidade.\",\"ja-JP\":\"AIに対するVimeoの取り組みと、コミュニティからのフィードバックの募集。\"},\"categories\":[{\"category\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:Reference\",\"id\":\"abfaa6a8703c49bda78368268f8a938b\",\"model\":\"blog-tags\"}},{\"category\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:Reference\",\"id\":\"9e7d4c2e003648d0addcad1d9a669237\",\"model\":\"blog-tags\"}}],\"headerImage\":{\"alt\":{\"Default\":\"How Vimeo is approaching AI, plus a call for feedback from our community.\",\"pt-BR\":\"Como o Vimeo está abordando a IA e um pedido de feedback para nossa comunidade.\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"ja-JP\":\"AIに対するVimeoの取り組みと、コミュニティからのフィードバックの募集。\",\"es\":\"Cómo Vimeo se está acercando a la IA, además de una llamada para recibir comentarios de nuestra comunidad.\"},\"url\":\"https://f.vimeocdn.com/cms-images/2024/04/Screenshot-2024-04-23-at-10.49.48 AM.jpg?w=1024?w=800\",\"caption\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\"}},\"tags\":[\"Vimeo HQ\"],\"url\":\"/blog/post/note-on-ai\"}}}},{\"post\":{\"model\":\"blog-posts\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:Reference\",\"id\":\"a67a14540b0c40cfbf0a6e7b08c0444e\",\"value\":{\"published\":\"published\",\"id\":\"a67a14540b0c40cfbf0a6e7b08c0444e\",\"name\":\"Introducing AI-Generated Content Labeling on Vimeo\",\"modelId\":\"6798149b6abb485aa72026a5e57b35b9\",\"data\":{\"title\":{\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo AI 생성 콘텐츠 레이블링 소개\",\"de-DE\":\"Einführung der Kennzeichnung von KI-generierten Inhalten auf Vimeo\",\"fr-FR\":\"Présentation de l'étiquetage du contenu généré par l'IA sur Vimeo\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"pt-BR\":\"Apresentando a rotulagem de conteúdo gerado por IA no Vimeo\",\"ja-JP\":\"Vimeo、AI生成コンテンツラベルを導入\",\"Default\":\"Introducing AI-Generated Content Labeling on Vimeo\",\"es\":\"Presentamos el etiquetado de contenido generado por IA en Vimeo\"},\"description\":{\"Default\":\"Vimeo is committed to trust and transparency in the ever-changing landscape of generative AI. As such, creators must label meaningfully manipulated content.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Dans un environnement d'IA générative en constante évolution, Vimeo s'engage à miser sur la confiance et la transparence. Ainsi, les créateurs doivent étiqueter un contenu qui a été manipulé de façon évidente.\",\"pt-BR\":\"O Vimeo tem um compromisso com a confiança e a transparência no cenário em constante mudança da IA generativa. Portanto, os criadores devem marcar conteúdo significativamente manipulado.\",\"de-DE\":\"Vimeo setzt sich für Vertrauen und Transparenz in der sich ständig verändernden Landschaft der generativen KI ein. Daher müssen die Creators signifikant manipulierte Inhalte kennzeichnen.\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"ja-JP\":\"絶えず変化する生成AI環境において、Vimeoは信頼と透明性の確保に取り組んでいます。そのためクリエイターは、意図的に合成または操作されたコンテンツにはその旨を示すラベルを付ける必要があります。\",\"es\":\"Vimeo se compromete a mantener la confianza y la transparencia en el dinámico mundo de la IA generativa. Por lo tanto, los creadores deben etiquetar el contenido manipulado de forma significativa.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo의 목표는 지속적으로 변화하는 생성형 AI 환경에서 신뢰와 투명성을 유지하는 것입니다. 이를 위해 모든 크리에이터는 조작이 적용된 콘텐츠에 라벨을 지정해야 합니다.\"},\"categories\":[{\"category\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:Reference\",\"id\":\"9e7d4c2e003648d0addcad1d9a669237\",\"model\":\"blog-tags\"}},{\"category\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:Reference\",\"id\":\"abfaa6a8703c49bda78368268f8a938b\",\"model\":\"blog-tags\"}}],\"headerImage\":{\"url\":\"https://f.vimeocdn.com/cms-images/2024/07/Blog_Header-2.jpg\",\"alt\":{\"pt-BR\":\"O Vimeo tem um compromisso com a confiança e a transparência no cenário em constante mudança da IA generativa. Portanto, os criadores devem marcar conteúdo significativamente manipulado.\",\"ja-JP\":\"絶えず変化する生成AI環境において、Vimeoは信頼と透明性の確保に取り組んでいます。そのためクリエイターは、意図的に合成または操作されたコンテンツにはその旨を示すラベルを付ける必要があります。\",\"es\":\"Vimeo se compromete a mantener la confianza y la transparencia en el dinámico mundo de la IA generativa. Por lo tanto, los creadores deben etiquetar el contenido manipulado de forma significativa.\",\"Default\":\"Vimeo is committed to trust and transparency in the ever-changing landscape of generative AI. As such, creators must label meaningfully manipulated content.\",\"ko-KR\":\"Vimeo의 목표는 지속적으로 변화하는 생성형 AI 환경에서 신뢰와 투명성을 유지하는 것입니다. 이를 위해 모든 크리에이터는 조작이 적용된 콘텐츠에 라벨을 지정해야 합니다.\",\"fr-FR\":\"Dans un environnement d'IA générative en constante évolution, Vimeo s'engage à miser sur la confiance et la transparence. Ainsi, les créateurs doivent étiqueter un contenu qui a été manipulé de façon évidente.\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\",\"de-DE\":\"Vimeo setzt sich für Vertrauen und Transparenz in der sich ständig verändernden Landschaft der generativen KI ein. Daher müssen die Creators signifikant manipulierte Inhalte kennzeichnen.\"},\"caption\":{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:LocalizedValue\"}},\"tags\":[],\"url\":\"/blog/post/introducing-ai-content-labeling\"}}}},{\"post\":{\"model\":\"blog-posts\",\"id\":\"cb0dcc1829e5490e82f382bd410a87ea\",\"@type\":\"@builder.io/core:Reference\"}}],\"blocks\":[{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/sdk:Element\",\"@version\":2,\"id\":\"builder-6647ace4d6ef4437be4def0a1c57d389\",\"component\":{\"name\":\"GlobalNavV3\",\"options\":{\"theme\":\"white\"},\"isRSC\":null}},{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/sdk:Element\",\"@version\":2,\"id\":\"builder-5a006f8f27674251a659ac1e3773d779\",\"component\":{\"name\":\"BlogNavBar\",\"options\":{},\"isRSC\":null}},{\"@type\":\"@builder.io/sdk:Element\",\"@version\":2,\"id\":\"builder-de9644bee2454ed6860a0e26a01a8dff\",\"meta\":{\"localizedTextInputs\":[\"srPaginationLabel\",\"srPageLabel\",\"srPrevLabel\",\"srNextLabel\"]},\"component\":{\"name\":\"BlogPostsDynamic\",\"options\":{\"limit\":24,\"offset\":0,\"showPagination\":true,\"showMoreButton\":false,\